Create a structure that will store information about the zodiac sign, with the name Znak. The Znak structure must contain the following fields:
name - surname, first name and patronymic;
zodiac - zodiac sign;
bday - birthday (an array of three numbers).

The program should be able to perform the following actions:

entering data from the keyboard to the book array, consisting of eight elements of the Znak type;
displaying on the screen information about people born in the month, the value of which is entered from the keyboard, if there are none, issue a corresponding message on the display.
sorting records by the name field;